  - key: mainmenu.gamemanajemen.rawimage.credit.scroll.view.viewport.content.credit.text
    english: 'THIRD-PERSON SHOOTERS PROTOTYPE GAME


      Created by

      Ikbal
      Gumilar


      Game Design

      Ikbal Gumilar


      Programming

      Ikbal
      Gumilar


