      Gumilar


      Inventory System

      Ikbal Gumilar


      UI Implementation

      Ikbal
      Gumilar


      Animation Setup

      Ikbal Gumilar


      Level Design

      Ikbal
      Gumilar



      ASSETS


      This prototype uses a combination of:

      Unity
      Asset Store assets

      Purchased assets

      Modified assets

      Original
      assets created for this project


      3D Models

      Unity Asset Store
      / Purchased Assets / Original Work


      Animations

      Unity Asset Store
      / Purchased Assets / Modified for this prototype


      Audio

      Unity
      Asset Store / Purchased Assets / Original Work


      Visual Effects

      Unity
      Asset Store / Purchased Assets / Original Work



      SPECIAL THANKS


      Thanks
      to everyone who tested, gave feedback,

      or supported the development
      of this prototype.



      DISCLAIMER


      This game is a prototype created
      for learning,

      testing gameplay systems, and development practice.


      Some
      assets used in this project may belong to their

      respective creators
      and are used according to their licenses.














      THANK YOU FOR
      PLAYING'
    indonesian: 'THIRD-PERSON SHOOTERS PROTOTYPE GAME


      Dibuat oleh

      Ikbal
      Gumilar


      Desain Game

      Ikbal Gumilar


      Pemrograman

