  - key: menu.play_game
    english: Play Game
    indonesian: Mulai Main
  - key: runtime.option.graphics
    english: Graphics
    indonesian: Grafis
  - key: runtime.option.controls
    english: Controls
    indonesian: Kontrol
  - key: runtime.option.audio
    english: Audio
    indonesian: Audio
  - key: runtime.option.graphics.info
    english: Select a graphics setting to see what it changes.
    indonesian: Pilih pengaturan grafis untuk melihat apa yang akan diubah.
  - key: runtime.option.controls.info
    english: View and adjust camera sensitivity, aim sensitivity, mouse inversion, and gameplay input references.
    indonesian: Lihat dan atur sensitivitas kamera, sensitivitas bidik, pembalikan mouse, dan referensi input gameplay.
  - key: runtime.option.audio.info
    english: Adjust master, music, and sound effect volume when the audio controls are available.
    indonesian: Atur volume master, musik, dan efek suara saat kontrol audio tersedia.
  - key: runtime.option.audio.unavailable
    english: Audio controls are not available yet. Create an Audio menu or Sound menu under Option to enable this tab.
    indonesian: Kontrol audio belum tersedia. Buat menu Audio atau Sound di dalam Option untuk mengaktifkan tab ini.
  - key: runtime.confirm.back.title
    english: Back to Main Menu?
    indonesian: Kembali ke Menu Utama?
  - key: runtime.confirm.back.info
    english: Current gameplay will be left.
    indonesian: Gameplay saat ini akan ditinggalkan.
  - key: runtime.confirm.back.button
    english: Back to Main Menu
    indonesian: Kembali ke Menu Utama
  - key: runtime.confirm.stay.button
    english: Stay
    indonesian: Tetap di Sini
  - key: runtime.option.display
    english: Display
    indonesian: Tampilan
  - key: runtime.option.display.info
    english: Screen output settings such as resolution, fullscreen mode, and V-Sync.
    indonesian: Pengaturan tampilan layar seperti resolusi, mode layar penuh, dan V-Sync.
  - key: runtime.option.resolution
    english: Resolution
    indonesian: Resolusi
  - key: runtime.option.resolution.info
    english: Changes the game output resolution. Higher resolutions look sharper but cost more GPU performance.
    indonesian: Mengubah resolusi output game. Resolusi lebih tinggi terlihat lebih tajam tetapi memakai performa GPU lebih besar.
  - key: runtime.option.fullscreen
    english: Full Screen
    indonesian: Layar Penuh
  - key: runtime.option.fullscreen.info
    english: Switches between fullscreen window mode and windowed mode. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Mengganti antara mode layar penuh dan mode jendela. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.vsync
    english: V-Sync
    indonesian: V-Sync
  - key: runtime.option.vsync.info
    english: Synchronizes rendering with the display refresh rate to reduce tearing. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Menyinkronkan render dengan refresh rate layar untuk mengurangi tearing. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.vegetation.physics
    english: Vegetation Physics
    indonesian: Fisika Vegetasi
  - key: runtime.option.vegetation.physics.info
    english: Controls foliage wind animation from Wind Zone and CTI shader wind. Turning it off freezes tree and billboard wind movement. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Mengatur animasi angin dedaunan dari Wind Zone dan shader wind CTI. Jika dimatikan, gerakan angin pohon dan billboard akan berhenti. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.quality
    english: Quality
    indonesian: Kualitas
  - key: runtime.option.quality.info
    english: Rendering quality settings that affect visual detail and performance.
    indonesian: Pengaturan kualitas render yang memengaruhi detail visual dan performa.
  - key: runtime.option.quality.preset
    english: Quality Preset
    indonesian: Preset Kualitas
  - key: runtime.option.quality.preset.info
    english: Applies one of Unity's project quality presets.
    indonesian: Menerapkan salah satu preset kualitas proyek Unity.
  - key: runtime.option.texture.quality
    english: Texture Quality
    indonesian: Kualitas Tekstur
  - key: runtime.option.texture.quality.info
    english: Controls texture mipmap quality. Lower settings reduce memory usage and texture sharpness.
    indonesian: Mengatur kualitas mipmap tekstur. Pengaturan lebih rendah mengurangi penggunaan memori dan ketajaman tekstur.
  - key: runtime.option.shadow.quality
    english: Shadow Quality
    indonesian: Kualitas Bayangan
  - key: runtime.option.shadow.quality.info
    english: Controls shadow rendering. Higher shadow quality improves depth but costs GPU performance.
    indonesian: Mengatur render bayangan. Kualitas bayangan lebih tinggi meningkatkan kedalaman visual tetapi memakai performa GPU lebih besar.
  - key: runtime.option.anti.aliasing
    english: Anti-Aliasing
    indonesian: Anti-Aliasing
  - key: runtime.option.anti.aliasing.info
    english: Reduces jagged edges. Unsupported methods will fall back to a supported option.
    indonesian: Mengurangi tepi bergerigi. Metode yang tidak didukung akan kembali ke opsi yang tersedia.
  - key: runtime.option.post.processing
    english: Post Processing
    indonesian: Post Processing
  - key: runtime.option.post.processing.info
    english: Camera effects that change the final rendered image.
    indonesian: Efek kamera yang mengubah hasil akhir gambar.
  - key: runtime.option.bloom
    english: Bloom
    indonesian: Bloom
  - key: runtime.option.bloom.info
    english: Adds glow around bright areas. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Menambahkan cahaya di sekitar area terang. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.motion.blur
    english: Motion Blur
    indonesian: Motion Blur
  - key: runtime.option.motion.blur.info
    english: Blends fast camera or object movement to create a smoother motion look. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Membaurkan gerakan kamera atau objek yang cepat agar terlihat lebih halus. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.depth.of.field
    english: Depth Of Field
    indonesian: Depth Of Field
  - key: runtime.option.depth.of.field.info
    english: Blurs areas outside the focus range for a camera lens effect. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Memburamkan area di luar fokus untuk efek lensa kamera. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.chromatic.aberration
    english: Chromatic Aberration
    indonesian: Chromatic Aberration
  - key: runtime.option.chromatic.aberration.info
    english: Adds subtle color fringing near image edges. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Menambahkan pinggiran warna halus di dekat tepi gambar. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
  - key: runtime.option.film.grain
    english: Film Grain
    indonesian: Film Grain
  - key: runtime.option.film.grain.info
    english: Adds a grain/noise overlay for a cinematic texture. Slider value 0 is On, 1 is Off.
    indonesian: Menambahkan lapisan grain/noise untuk tekstur sinematik. Nilai slider 0 berarti On, 1 berarti Off.
